  <summary date="2021-12-07T13:33:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Elaine M. Checketts Military Families Act

This bill directs the Department of Defense to amend regulations to ensure that parental leave that has already been approved for a member of the Armed Forces who is a primary or secondary caregiver may not be terminated upon the death of the child for whom the leave was taken.</summary>
